README

Simple UDP -> TCP proxy

proxy.js
to launch proxy.js two arguments will need to be provided. The first argument is the udp port to listen on. The second argument is tcp port to forward on.

node proxy.js [udp port] [tcp port]

tcpListener.js
an addition script that can be used to test proxy. can be lauched with a single command line argument with the tcp port to listen on.

node tcpListener.js [tcp port]